hadiths[91]{hadithnumber,text}:
3652,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad main apni biwi ko jabke wo haaiza thi, talaaq de di. Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : usey hukm do ke wo us se rujoo karey, phir usey rehney de yahan tak ke wo paak ho jaey (paki shuru ho jaey), phir usey haiz aa jaey, phir wo paak ho jaey. phir agar wo chahey to iske baad usey apne paas rakhey aur agar chahey to us se mujamiat (sambhog) karne se pahley talaaq de dey . yahi wo iddat hai jiska Allah ne hukm diya hai ke iske mutabiq aurton ko talaaq di jaey."
3653,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur ibne- Rumeh ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz Yahya ke hain. padhi. Quteba ne kaha : hamein Leis ne hadis sunai aur doosrey donon ne kaha : hamein Lais-bin-Sad ne Naafe se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne apni biwi ko jab wo haiz ki haalat mein thi aik talaaq di, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke wo us se rujoo karein, phir usey (apne paas ( rokein yahan tak ke wo paak ho jaey, phir unke yahaan usey dobara haiz aaey, phir usey mohlat dein yahan tak ke wo ( phir se) apne haiz se paak ho jaey. iske baad agar usey talaaq dena chaahein to paki ke zamaney mein, iske sath mujamiat (sambhog) karne se pahley usey talaaq dein. yahi wo iddat hai jiska Allah ne hukm diya hai ke iske mutabiq aurton ko talaaq di jaey. ibne-Rumeh ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kiya : Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se jab is (masle) ke barey mein sawal kiya jata to wo unmein se kisi se kehtey : agar tum ne apni biwi ko aik ya do martaba talaaq di hai (to rujoo karo). kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey iska hukm diya tha aur agar tum usey teen talaaqein de chukey ho to wo tum par haram ho gaee hai. yahan tak ke wo tumharey siwa kisi aur shauhar se nikah kare. tum ne is hukm mein, jo usney tumhari biwi ki talaaq ke barey main tumhen diya hai, Allah ki nafarmani ki hai. Imam Muslim (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : Leis ne apne (riwaayat ki hui) qaul aik talaaq (ko mehfooz rakhney aur bayan karne ke mamley) mein bahut achchha kaam kiya hai."
3654,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak main apni biwi ko jab wo haiz ki haalat mein thi, talaaq de di. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batai to aap ne farmaya : usey hukm do ke us se rujoo karey phir usey (apne paas rakh) chhodey yahan tak ke wo paak ho jaey. phir usey doosra haiz aaey, iske baad jab wo paak ho jaey to mubashrat karne se pahley usey talaaq de ya usey apne paas rakhey. bila shubah yahi wo iddat hai jiska Allah Taala ne hukm diya hai ke iske mutabiq aurton ko talaaq di jaey. Ubaidullah ne kaha : maine Naafe se puchha : talaaq ka kya kiya gaya? unhon-ne jawab diya : wo aik thi, usko shumaar kiya gaya."
3655,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur ibne- Musanna ne bhi hamein yahi hadis sunai, un donon ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, taaham (phir bhi) unhon-ne Naafe se Ubaidullah ke sawal ka tazkira nahi kiya. ibne-Musanna ne apni riwayat mein (usey lota ley) kaha, aur Abu-Bakar ne : (is se rujoo karey) kaha."
3656,"Ayub ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein talaaq de di. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (iske barey mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kiya, to aap ne unhein hukm diya ke wo ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) is aurat se rujoo karey, phir usey mohlat de yahan tak ke usey doosra haiz aaey, phir usey mohlat de yahan tak ke wo paak ho jaey, phir usey chhooney (mujamiat karne) se pahley talaaq de. yahi wo iddat hai jiska Allah Taala ne hukm diya hai ke iske mutabiq aurton ko talaaq di jaey. (Naafe ne) kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se jab us aadmi ke barey mein puchha jata jo apni biwi ko haalatey-haiz mein talaaq de deta hai to wo kehtey : agar tum ne aik ya do talaaqein di hain (to rujoo kar saktey ho kyonke ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya tha ke us se rujoo karein, phir usey mohlat dein yahan tak ke usey doosra haiz aaey, ( farmaya : ( phir usey mohlat dein yahan tak ke wo paak ho jaey, phir us se mujamiat (sambhog) karne se pahley usey talaaq dein. aur agar tum ne teen talaaqein di hain to tum ne apne rab ke hukm mein jo usney tumhari biwi ki talaaq ke hawale se tumhen diya hai, uski nafarmani ki hai aur (ab) wo tum se ( mustaqil taur par) juda ho gaee hai."
3657,"imam Zohri ke bhatijey Muhammad ne hamein apne chacha Zohri se hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine apni biwi ko is haalat mein talaaq di ke wo haaiza thi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sakht ghussey mein aaey, phir farmaya : usey hukm do ke us se rujoo karey taake usey us haiz ke siwa jis mein us ne usey talaaq di hai doosra haiz shuru ho jaey. iske baad agar wo usey talaaq dena chahey to usey (doosrey haiz ke baad) paak honey ki haalat mein, mubashrat karne se pahley talaaq de. yahi iddat ke mutabiq talaaq hai jis tarah Allah ne hukm diya hai. aur Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne usey aik talaaq di thi aur uski wo talaaq shumaar ki gaee aur Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne, jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya tha, us se rujoo kiya."
3658,"Zubaidi ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki, lekin unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine us se rujoo kar liya aur uski wo talaaq shumaar kar li gaee jo maine usey di thi."
3659,"abu-Talha ke aazad karda ghulam Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ne Salim se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne apni biwi ko jabke wo haaiza thi, talaaq de di. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kahi to aap ne farmaya : usey hukm do ke wo us ( mutallaqa biwi ( se rujoo karey, phir usey paki ki haalat mein ya haalate-hamal mein talaaq de. ( hamal mein talaaq di jaeygi to waza' hamal tak aasani se iddat ka shumaar ho sakega."
3660,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne apni biwi ko jabke wo haaiza thi talaaq di, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein puchha to aap ne farmaya : usey hukm do ke us se rujoo karey yahan tak ke wo ( haiz se) paak ho jaey, phir usey dobara haiz aa jaey, phir paak ho jaey, phir iske baad usey talaaq de ya (apne paas ( rok ley."
3661,"Ismail-bin-Ibrahim ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibne-Sirin se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine bees-saal twaqquf kiya (thehra raha). mujhey aisey log jinhein main muttahim (jis par jhoot waigheira ka ilzaam laga ho) nahi samajhta tha hadis bayan kartey rahe ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni biwi ko jabke wo haaiza thi teen talaaqein de-di to unhein us se rujoo karne ka hukm diya gaya. maine ye kiya ke main unhein muttahim nahi karta tha. lekin hadis (ki haqiqat ( ko bhi nahi janta tha. yahan tak ke meri mulaqat abu-ghillaab Younus-bin-Juber Bahili se hui. wo bahut zabt waley they. ( hadis ko bahut achi tarah yad rakhney waley they) unhon-ne mujhey hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne khud ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha tha, unhon-ne unko hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein aik talaaq di thi to unhein hukm diya gaya ke wo us se rujoo karein. kaha : maine kaha : kya usey talaaq shumaar kiya gaya? unhon-ne jawab diya : kyon nahi ! agar koi ( aadmi ( khud hi ( sahi tareeqey par talaaq deney se) aajiz aa gaya ho aur) haalatey-haiz mein talaaq de kar) himaaqat se kaam liya ho (to kya talaaq na hogi.)"
3662,"Hammad ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum kiya to aap ne unhein hukm diya (ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ye karein.)"
3663,"Abdul-Waris-bin-Abdus-Samad ke dada Abdul-Waris-bin-Saeed ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath (yahi) riwayat bayan ki aur (apni) hadis mein kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein sawal kiya to aap ne unhein hukm diya ke wo ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) us se rujoo karey yahan tak ke usey paki ki haalat mein mujamiat (sambhog) kiye baghair talaaq de, aur kaha : wo usey iddat ke shuruat mein talaaq de. (yani us paki ki shuruat mein jis se iddat shumaar honi hai."
3664,"Yunus ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se, unhon-ne Younus-bin-Juber se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aik aadmi ne apni biwi ko haalate haiz mein talaaq di hai? to unhon-ne kaha : kya tum Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko jantey ho? us ne apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein talaaq di thi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur aap se malum kiya to aap ne usey (ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko) hukm diya ke wo us se rujoo karey. phir wo (aurat agar usey dusri paki mein mujamiat (sambhog) kiye baghair talaaq di jaey to wahan se) aagey iddat shumaar kare. kaha : maine un ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se puchha : agar koi aadmi apni biwi ko haalate-haiz mein talaaq de to kya us talaaq ko shumaar kiya jaeyga? kaha : unhon-ne kaha : to (aur) kya? agar wo khud hi ( sahi tariqa ikhtiyar karne se) aajiz raha aur us ne himaaqat se kaam liya (to kya talaaq shumaar na hogi.)"
3665,"Qatada se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : maine Younus-bin-Juber se suna unhon-ne kaha maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : maine apni biwi ko haalate-haiz mein talaaq di, is par Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko ye baat batai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo us se rujoo karey, iske baad jab wo paak ho jaey to agar wo chahey usey talaaq de dey. (Younus ne) kaha : maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap us talaaq ko shumaar karengey? unhon-ne kaha : is se kya cheez rukawat hai? tumhari kya raey hai? agar wo khud (sahi tariqa ikhtiyar karne se) aajiz raha aur naadaani wala kaam kiya (to talaaq kyon shumaar na hogi !)"
3666,"Abdul-Malik ne Anas-bin-Sirin se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unki us biwi ke barey mein sawal kiya jisey unhon-ne talaaq di thi. unhon-ne kaha : maine usey haalate-haiz mein talaaq di thi. maine ye baat Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko batai to unhon-ne yahi baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batai. is par aap ne farmaya : usey hukm do ke wo us se rujoo karey aur jab wo paak ho jaey to usey uski paki mein talaaq de. kaha : maine us ( biwi ( se rujoo kya, phir iske paki mein usey talaaq di. maine puchha : aap ne wo talaaq shumaar ki jo usey haalate haiz mein di thi? unhon-ne jawab diya : main usey kyon shumaar na karta? agar main khud hi ( sahi tariqa apnaaney se) aajiz raha tha aur himaaqat se kaam liya tha (to kya talaaq shumaar na hogi !)"
3667,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Anas-bin-Sirin se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine apni biwi ko us haalat mein talaaq di ke wo haaiza thi, is par Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko bataya to aap ne farmaya : usey hukm do ke us se rujoo karey, phir jab wo paak ho jaey to tab usey talaaq de. maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap ne us talaaq ko shumaar kiya tha? unhon-ne kaha : to (aur ( kya !"
3668,"Khalid-bin-Haaris aur Behaz donon ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad se hadis bayan ki, lekin un donon ki hadis mein (us se rujoo karne ki bajaey) (wo usko lota ley) hai. aur un donon ki hadis mein ye bhi hai, kaha : maine unse puchha : kya aap us talaaq ko shumaar karengey ? unhon-ne jawab diya : to (aur ( kya !"
3669,"(Abdullah) ibne-Taaus ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unse aisey aadmi ke barey mein sawal kiya ja raha tha jisne apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein talaaq di. unhon-ne kaha : kya tum Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko jantey ho? usne kaha : haan , unhon-ne kaha : unhon-ne apni biwi ko haiz mein talaaq de di thi. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaey aur aapko us khabar se aagah kiya. aap ne unhein hukm diya ke wo us se rujoo kare. ( ibne- Taaus ne) kaha : maine apne walid ko is se zyada bayan kartey huey nahi suna."
3670,"Hujjaj-bin-Muhammad ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne azzah ke Maula Abdur-Rehman-bin-aiman se suna, wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se poochh rahe they aur abu-Zubair bhi ye baat sun rahe they ke aap ki us aadmi ke barey mein kya raey hai jisne apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein talaaq de di? unhon-ne jawab diya : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney main apni biwi ko haalate-haiz mein talaaq di thi to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kiya aur bataya : Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein talaaq de di hai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : wo us se rujoo kare. chunanche unhon-ne us se rujoo kar liya, aur aap ne farmaya : jab wo paak ho jaey to usey talaaq de ya (apne yahaan basaaey ( rakhey. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye aayat ( tilawat farmai : aey Nabi ! jab aap log aurton ko talaaq dein to unhein unki iddat ( shuru karne) ke waqt talaaq dein."
3671,"abu-Aasim ne ibne-Juraij se, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se usi waqiey ke mutabiq riwayat ki."
3672,"Abdur-Razzaq ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, (kaha : ( mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Urwa ke Maula Abdur-Rehman-bin-aiman se suna, wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se poochh rahe they, aur abu-Zubair bhi sun rahe they. jis tarah Hajjaj ki hadis hai aur us ( hadis) mein kuchh izafa bhi hai. Imam Muslim (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : unhon-ne jo Maula Urwa kaha hai, usmein ghalati ki, wo Maula azzah they."
3673,"Mamar ne hamein ibne-Taaus se khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid ( Taaus-bin-kaisaan ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ahad mein aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat ke) shuruati ( do saalon tak ( ikatthi ( teen talaaqein aik shumaar hoti thi. phir Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : logon ne aisey kaam mein jald bazi shuru kar di hai jis mein unke liye tahammul aur soch vichaar ( zaroori ( tha. agar ham is (jaldi) ko un par Nafiz kar dein (to shayad wo tahammul se kaam lena shuru kar dein ). iske baad unhon-ne isey un par Nafiz kar diya. (ikatthi teen talaaqon ko teen shumaar karne lagey.)"
3674,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein khabar di, kaha : mujhey ibne-Taaus ne apne walid ( Taaus-bin-kaisaan ( se khabar di ke abu-Sahbaa ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap jantey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ahad mein, aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat ke) shuruati ( teen saalon tak teen talaaqon ko aik shumaar kiya jata hai? to Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : haan."
3675,"Ibrahim-bin-Maisra ne Taaus se riwayat ki ke abu-Sahbaa ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap apne nawaadir qimtee (jin se aksar log be-khabar hain) fatwon mein se koi cheez inayat karein. kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ahad mein teen talaaqein aik nahi thin? unhon-ne jawab diya : yaqinan aisey hi tha, iske baad jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka zamana aaya to logon ne pai-dar-pai (ghalat tareeqey se aik sath teen) talaaqein dena shuru kar dein. to unhon-ne is baat ko un par laagu kar diya."
3676,"Hisham , yani dustwaai ( kapdey waale) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Yahya-bin-Kasir ne Yala-bin-Hakim se hadis bayan kartey huey likh bheja, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo ( biwi ko apne uper ( haram karne ke barey mein kaha kartey they : ye qism hai jiska wo kaffara dega aur Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : yaqinan tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki zindagi ( mein behtreen namoona hai."
3677,"Muawiya-bin-Salaam ne hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se hadis bayan ki ke Yala-bin-Hakim ne unhein khabar di, unhein Saeed-bin-Jubair ne khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna : unhon-ne kaha : jab koi aadmi apni biwi ko apne uper haram thehra ley to ye qism hai jiska wo kaffara dega, aur kaha : bila shubah tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki zindagi ( mein behtreen namoona hai."
3678,"Ubaid-bin-Umair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, wo bata rahi thin ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zainab-binte ( Jahash ( (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan thahartey aur unke paas se shehad nosh farmatey they : kaha : main aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne ittifaq kiya ke ham mein se jiske paas bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (pahley ( tashrif laaein, wo kahey : mujhey aap se maghaafeer ki bo mehsus ho rahi hai. kya aap ne maghaafeer khaai hai? aap unmein se aik ke paas tashrif le gaey to unhon-ne aap ke samney yahi baat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : balke maine Zainab-bint-Jahash ke yahan se shehad piyaa hai. aur aainda hargiz nahi piyun ga . is par) Quraan ( nazil hua :'' aap kyon haram thehratey hain jo Allah ne aap ke liye halal kiya hai?'' us farman tak : agar tum donon tauba karo. padhi. ye Aaisha aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke liye kaha gaya. padhi. aur jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni kisi biwi se raaz ki baat kahi us se murad (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye farman ( hai : balke maine shehad piyaa hai."
3679,"abu-Usama ne hamein Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meethi cheez aur shehad ko pasand farmatey they, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz padhtey to apni tamam beeviyon ke yahan chakkar lagaatey aur unke qareeb hotey , ( aisa hua ke) aap Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaey to unke yahan aap us se zyada ( der ke liye) rukey jitna aap ( kisi biwi ke paas ( ruka kartey they. un (Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ( ko unke khandan ki kisi aurat ne shehad ka ( bharaa hua) aik bartan hadiya kya tha to unhon-ne usmein se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko shehad pilaya . maine (dil mein) kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham aap (ko zyada der qiyam se rokney (ke liye zaroor koi heela karengi, chunanche maine is baat ka zikr Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) se kya, aur kaha : jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumharey yahan tashrif laaengey to tumharey qareeb hongey, (is waqt) tum unse kehna : Allah ke rasool! kya aap ne maghaafeer khaai hai? wo tumhen jawab dengey, nahi ! to tum unse kehna : ye bo kaisi hai? . padhi. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ye baat intihai nagawar guzarti thi ke aap se bo mehsus ki jaey. padhi. is par wo tumhen jawab dengey : mujhey Hafsa ne shehad pilaya tha, to tum unse kehna ( phir ( uski makkhi ne arfat ( boti) ka ras choosa hoga. mein bhi aap se yahi baat kahungi aur Safiya tum bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi kehna ! jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan tashrif le gaey, ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : Sauda (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain is zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi haqiqi maabood nahi ! aap abhi darwazey par hi they ke main tumhari malaamat ke dar se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko buland awaz se wo baat kehney hi lagi thi jo tum ne mujh se kahi thi, phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qareeb huey to Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! kya aap ne maghaafeer khaai hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi. unhon-ne kaha : to ye bo kaisi hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey Hafsa ne shehad pilaya tha. unhon-ne kaha : phir uski makkhi ne arfat ka ras choosa hoga. iske baad jab aap mere yahan tashrif laaey, to maine bhi aap se yahi baat kahi, phir aap Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey, to unhon-ne bhi yahi baat kahi, iske baad aap Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan (dobara) tashrif laey to unhon-ne kaha : kya aapko shehad pesh na karun to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi, mujhey uski zarurat nahi. (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : Sauda (Raziallahu anha) kehney lagin, Subhan-Allah! Allah ki qasam! ham ne aapko us se mahroom kar diya hai. to maine unse kaha : khamosh rahen. Abu-Ishaq Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Hasan-bin-Bishr bin-Qasim ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein abu-Usama ne bilkul isi tarah hadis bayan ki."
3680,Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
3681,"ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm diya gaya ke wo apni beeviyon ko ikhtiyar dein to aap ne ( uski ( shuruaat mujh se ki, aur farmaya : main tum se aik baat karne laga hun. tumharey liye is baat mein koi harj nahi ke tum apne waalidain se mashwara karne tak ( jawab diye mein) ujlat se kaam na lo. unhon-ne kaha : aapko b-khoobi ilm tha ke mere waalidain mujhey kabhi aap se juda honey ka mashwara nahi dengey. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah Taala ne farmaya hai : aey Nabi ! apni beeviyon se keh dijiye ki agar tum duniya ki zindagi aur uski zeenat chahti ho to aao main tumhen ( duniya ka ( saaz w saman dun aur tumhen achai ke sath rukhsat kar dun aur agar tum Allah aur uska rasool aur aakhirat ka ghar chahti ho to Allah ne tum mein se nek kaam karne waaliyon ke liye ajr azeem taiyaar kar rakha hai. ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : maine kaha : unmein se kis baat main apne waalidain se mashwara karun? main to Allah, uska rasool aur aakhirat ka ghar chahti hun. kaha : phir Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tamam beeviyon ne wahi kya jo maine kya tha."
3682,"Ibad bin Ibad ne hamein Aasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Muaz adwiya se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab ham mein se kisi biwi ki baari ka din hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( kisi aur biwi ke yahan janey ke liye) ham se ijazat letey they, halanke ye aayat nazil ho chuki thi : aap unmein se jisey chaahein (khud se) alag rakhein aur jisey chaahein apne paas jagah dein. to Muaza ne unse puchha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aap se ijazat letey to aap unse kya kehti thin? unhon-ne jawab diya : main kehti thi : agar ye ( ikhtiyar ( mere sipurd hai to main apne aap par kisi ko tarjeeh nahi deti ."
3683,( Abdullah ( bin-Mubarak ne kaha : hamein Aasim ne isi sanad se usi ke ham-mana khabar di.
3684,"Absar ne hamein Ismail bin abi Khalid se khabar di, unhon-ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Masruq se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : (jab) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein (alehda ho janey ka ( ikhtiyar diya tha, to ham ne usey talaaq shumar nahi kya."
3685,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne isi sanad ke sath Masruq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab meri ahliya ne mujhey pasand kar liya to iske baad mujhey koi parwah nahi ke main usey aik baar, so baar ya aik hazaar bar ikhtiyar dun. bila shubah maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se malum kya tha to unhon-ne jawab diya : bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ikhtiyar diya tha to kya wo talaaq thi! ( nahi thi.)"
3686,"Shoba ne hamein Aasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko (sath rehney ya alehda ho janey ka ( ikhtiyar diya tha aur wo talaaq nahi thi."
3687,"Sufiyan ne Aasim Ahwal aur Ismail bin abi Khalid se, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ikhtiyar diya to ham ne aapko ikhtiyar kya (chun liya) aur aap ne usey talaaq shumar nahi kya."
3688,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Muslim se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ikhtiyar diya to ham ne aapko ikhtiyar kar liya aur aap ne usey ham par (talaaq wghaira) kuchh shumar nahi kya."
3689,"Ismail bin Zakariya ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ibrahim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, (neez Ismail ne) Aamash se, unhon-ne Muslim (ibne-sabeeh) se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se isi ki tarah riwayat ki."
3690,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaey, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir honey ki ijazat maang rahe they. unhon-ne logon ko aap ke darwazey par baithey huey paya. unmein se kisi ko ijazat nahi mili thi. kaha : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ijazat mili to wo andar dakhil ho gaey, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaey, unhon-ne ijazat mangi, unhein bhi ijazat mil gaee, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ghamgeen aur khamosh baithey huey paya, aap ki beeviyan aap ke ird-gird thin. kaha : to unhon (Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : main zaroor koi aisi baat karunga jis se main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hansaaunga. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! kash! ke aap binte- khaarija ko dekhtey jab us ne mujh se nafqa ka sawal kya to main uski taraf badha aur uski gardan daba di. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans padey aur farmaya : ye bhi mere ird-gird baithi hain, jaisey tum dekh rahe ho, aur mujh se nafqa maang rahi hain. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf uthey aur unki gardan par zarb lagana chahtey they aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf badhey aur wo unki gardan par maarna chahtey they, ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un donon ko us se rok diya. musnad Ahmed : 3/328) aur donon keh rahe they : tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us cheez ka sawal karti ho jo unke paas nahi hai. wo kehney lagin : Allah ki qasam! aaj ke baad ham kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisi cheez ka mutalba nahi karengi jo aap ke paas na hogi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik maah ya untees din tak ke liye unse alehadgi ikhtiyar kar li. phir aap par ye aayat nazil hui : aey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap apni beeviyon se keh do. yahan tak ke yahan pahunch gaey : tum mein se neki karne waliyon ke liye bada ajr hai. (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aap ne shuruat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ki aur farmaya : aey Aaisha ! main tumharey samney aik mamla pesh kar raha hun aur pasand karta hun ke tum, apne waalidain se mashwara kar leney tak usmein jaldi na karna. unhon-ne kaha : kya main aap ke barey mein, Allah ke rasool! apne waalidain se mashwara karungi! balke main to Allah , iske rasool aur aakhirat ke ghar ko chunti hun, aur aap se ye darkhast karti hun ke jo maine kaha hai, aap apni beeviyon mein se kisi ko uski khabar na dein. aap ne farmaya : mujh se jo bhi poochhegi main usey bata dunga, Allah Taala ne mujhey sakhti karne wala aur logon ke liye mushkilat dhoondney wala bana kar nahi bheja, balke Allah ne mujhey taleem dene wala aur aasani karne wala bana kar bheja hai."
3691,"Samak abu-Zameel se riwayat hai, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( mujhey Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mujhey umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon se alehadgi ikhtiyar farmai, kaha : main masjid mein dakhil hua to logon ko dekha wo (pareshani aur tafakkur mein) kankariyan zamin par mar rahe hain, aur keh rahe hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai, ye waqia unhein pardey ka hukm diye janey se pahley ka hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine (dil mein) kaha : aaj main us mamley ko jaan kar rahunga. unhon-ne kaha : main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya, aur kaha : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti! tum us had tak pahunch chuki ho ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko azeeyat do? unhon-ne jawab diya : Khattab ke betey ! aap ka mujh se kya waasta? aap apni gathri (ya thaila wghaira jis mein qeemti saaz w saman sanbhaal kar rakha jata hai yani apni beti Hafsa (Raziallahu anha)) ki fikr karein. unhon-ne kaha : phir main (apni beti) Hafsa binte-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha : Hafsa! kya tum us had tak pahunch gaee ho ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef do? Allah ki qasam! tumhen khub malum hai ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tum se mohabbat nahi rakhtey. agar main na hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumhen talaaq de detey. ( meri ye baat sun kar) wo buri tarah se roney lagin. maine unse puchha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kahan hain? unhon-ne jawab diya : wo apne baala khaney par saman rakhney wali jagah mein hain. main wahan gaya to dekha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ghulam Rabaah (Raziallahu anhu) chaubaarey ki chaukhat ke nichey wali lakdi par betha hai. us ne apne donon paon lakdi ki suraakh daar seedhi par latka rakhey hain. wo khajoor ka aik tanaa tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par) qadam rakh kar) chadhtey aur utartey they. maine awaz di, Ribah ! mujhey apne paas, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein, hazir honey ki ijazat ley do. Ribah (Raziallahu anhu) ne bula khaney ki taraf nazar ki, phir mujhey dekha aur kuchh na kaha, maine phir kaha : Ribah ! mujhey apne paas , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein, hazir honey ki ijazat ley do, Ribah (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( dobara ( bula khaney ki taraf nigaah uthai , phir mujhey dekha, aur kuchh na kaha, phir maine apni awaz buland ki aur kaha : aey Ribah ! mujhey apne paas, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein, hazir honey ki ijazat ley do, mera khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne samjha hai ke main Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki (sifarish karne ki) khaatir aaya hun, Allah ki qism ! agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey uski gardan udaaney ka hukm dein to main uski gardan uda doonga, aur maine apni awaz ko) khub ( buland kya, to usne mujhey ishara kya ke uper chadh aao. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, aap aik chataai par letey huey they, main baith gaya, aap ne apna izaar durust kya aur aap (ke jism) par iske ilawa aur kuchh na tha aur chataai ne aap ke jism par nishan daal diye they. maine apni aankhon se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saman ke kamrey mein dekha to sirf muththi bhar jo aik saa ke barabar hongey, jau aur kamrey ke aik koney mein itni hi keekar ki chhaal dekhi. iske ilawa aik ghair dabaghat shuda chamda latkaa hua tha. kaha : to meri aankhen beh padin, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : ibne-khattaab! tumhen kya cheez rula rahi hai? maine kaha : Allah ke Nabi ! main kyon na roon? us chataai ne aap ke jism At-har par nishan daal diye hain, aur ye aapka saman rakhney ka kamra hai, usmein wahi kuchh hai jo mujhey nazar aa raha hai, aur qaisar w Kisraa nehron aur phalon ke darmyan (shaandaar zindagi Basar kar rahe) hain, jabke aap to Allah ke rasool aur uski chuni hui hasti hain, aur ye aap ka Sara saman hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ibne-khattaab ! kya tumhen pasand nahi ke hamarey liye aakhirat ho aur unke liye duniya ho? maine kaha : kyon nahi ! kaha : jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua tha to aapkey chehrey par ghussa dekh raha tha, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! aapko (apni ( beeviyon ki haalat ki bina par kya dushwari hai? agar aap ne unhein talaaq de di hai to Allah aap ke sath hai, uske Farishtey, Jibreel, Mikaail, main, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur tamam momin aap ke sath hain. aur main Allah ka shukr ada karta hun ke maine kam hi koi baat kahi , magar maine ummeed ki ke Allah meri is baat ki tasdeeq farma dega jo main keh raha hun. ( chunanche aisey hi hua) aur ye takhyeer ki aayat nazil ho gaee : agar wo (Nabi ( tum sab ( beeviyon ( ko talaaq de dein to qareeb hai ke unka rab , unhein tum se behtar beeviyan badley mein de. aur agar tum donon unke khilaf aik doosrey ki madad karogi, to Allah khud unka nigahban hai, aur Jibreel aur Saleh momin aur uske baad tamam Farishtey (unke) madadgar hain. Aaisha binte- abi-Bakr aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anhunna) donon Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tamam beeviyon ke muqaabley mein aik doosrey ka sath deti thin. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya aap ne unko talaaq de di hai? aap ne farmaya : nahi. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! main masjid mein dakhil hua tha to log kankariyan zamin par mar rahe they, aur keh rahe they : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai. kya main utar kar unhein bata dun ke aap ne un ( beeviyon ( ko talaaq nahi di? aap ne farmaya : haan, agar chaho. main musalsal aap se guftgu karta raha yahan tak ke aap ke chehrey se ghussa door ho gaya, aur yahan tak ke aap ke hont khuley aur aap hansey. aap ke samney waley daant sab insanon se zyada khoobsurat they. phir Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (bala khaney se nichey) utrey. main taney ko thaamtey huey utra aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisey utrey jaisey zamin par chal rahe hon, aap ne taney ko hath tak na lagaya . maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap bula khaney mein 29 din rahe hain. aap ne farmaya : mahina 29 din ka hota hai. chunanche main masjid ke darwazey par khada hua, aur buland awaz se pukar kar kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq nahi di, aur) phir ( ye aayat nazil hui : aur jab unke paas amn ya khof ki koi khabar aati hai to usey mashhoor kar detey hain, aur agar wo usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf aur apne maamlaat sanbhalney walon ki taraf lota detey, to wo log jo unmein usse asl matlab akhaz kartey hain usey zaroor jaan letey. to main hi tha jisne us mamley ki asl haqiqat ko akhaz kya, aur Allah Taala ne takhyeer ki aayat nazil farmai."
3692,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne kaha : mujhey Yahya ne Ubaid bin Hunain se khabar di ke unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : maine saal bhar intizar kya, main Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se aik aayat ke barey mein malum karna chahta tha magar unki haibat ki wjah se unse sawal karne ki himmat na paata tha, yahan tak ke wo Haj karne ke liye rawana huey, main bhi unke sath nikla, jab lautey to ham rastey mein kisi jagah they ke wo qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye peelu ke darakht ki taraf chaley gaey, main unke intizar mein thehar gaya, yahan tak ke wo farigh ho gaey, phir main unke sath chal padaa, maine kaha : ameerul-momeneen ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein se wo kon si 2 khawateen thin jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khilaf ekaa kar liya tha? unhon-ne jawab diya : wo Hafsa aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) thin. maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! main aik saal se iske barey mein aap se poochhna chahta tha magar aap ke raub ki wjah se himmat na paata tha. unhon-ne kaha : aisa nahi karna, jo baat bhi tum samjho ke mujhey ilm hai, iske barey mein mujh se poochh liya karo, agar main janta hua to tumhen bata doonga . kaha : aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! jab ham jahiliyat ke zamaney mein they, to aurton ko kisi shumaar mein na rakhtey they, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne unke barey mein jo nazil kya, so nazil kya, aur jo (martaba) unhein dena tha so diya. unhon-ne kaha : aik martaba main kisi mamley mein laga hua tha, iske mutaalliq soch bichaar kar raha tha ke mujhey meri biwi ne kaha : agar aap aisa aisa kar lein (to behtar hoga.) maine usey jawab diya : tumhen us se kya sarokaar? aur yahan (is mamley mein) tumhen kya dilchaspi hai? aur aik kaam jo main karna chahta hun usmein tumhara takalluf (zabardasti taang adaana) kaisa? usne mujhey jawab diya : ibne-khattaab! aap par tajjub hai ! aap ye nahi chahtey ke aap ke aagey baat ki jaey, jabke aap ki beti Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisey palat kar jawab deti hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) din bhar us se naraz rahtey hain. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main (usi waqt) apni chadar pakadta hun aur apni jagah se nikal khada hota hun, yahan tak ke Hafsa ke paas pahunchta hun. ja kar maine us se kaha : bitiya! tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisey jawab deti ho ke wo Sara din naraz rehtey hain. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne jawab diya : Allah ki qasam! ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jawab de leti hain. maine kaha : jaan lo main tumhen Allah ki saza aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki narazgi se dara raha hun, meri beti ! tumhen wo ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) apne rawaiye ki bina par) dhokey mein na daal de jisey apne husn aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki apne se mohabbat par naaz hai. phir main nikla yahan tak ke Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aaya, kyonke meri unse qarabat dari thi. maine unse baat ki to Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey jawab diya : ibne-khattaab tum par tajjub hai ! tum har kaam mein dakhal andazi kartey ho yahan tak ke tum chahtey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur unki beeviyon ke beech bhi dakhal do? unhon-ne mujhey is tarah aadey hathon liya ke jo ( azm ( main (dil mein) pa raha tha (ke mein paak beeviyon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney jawab deney se rok loonga ( mujhey tod kar us se alag kar diya. chunanche main unke yahan se nikal aaya. mera aik Ansari sathi tha, jab main (aap ki majlis se) ghair hazir hota to wo mere paas ( wahan ki) khabar laata aur jab wo ghair hazir hota to main uske paas khabar ley aata. ham us zamaney mein ghassan ke badshahon mein se aik badshah se dar rahe they. hamein bataya gaya tha ke wo ham par chadhai karna chahtey hain. us (ki wjah ( se hamarey seeney ( andeshon se) bharey huey they. ( achcha aik din) mera Ansari dost aa kar darwaza khatkhataney laga aur kehney laga : kholo , kholo ! maine puchha : ghassani aa gaya hai? usne kaha is se bhi zyada sangeen mamla hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon se alehadgi ikhtiyar kar li hai. maine kaha : Hafsa aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki naak khaak aalud ho! phir main apne kapdey lekar nikal khada hua, yahan tak ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein) hazir hua. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne bula khaney mein they jis par seedhi ke zariey chadh kar jana hota tha, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aik siyah faam ghulam seedhi ke sirey par betha hua tha. maine kaha : ye umr hai) khidmat mein haziri ki ijazat chahta hai) , to mujhey ijazat ata hui. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ye saari baat bayan ki, jab main Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki baat par pahuncha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskura diye. aap aik chataai par) letey huey) they, aap ke) jism Mubarak (aur us ( chataai) ke darmyan kuchh na tha. aap ke sar ke nichey chamdey ka aik takiya tha jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi. aap ke paon ke qareeb keekar ki chhaal ka chhota sa gatha padaa tha aur aap ke sar ke qareeb kuchh kachchey chamdey latkey huey they. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pahlu par chataai ke nishan dekhey to ro padaa. aap ne puchha : tumhen kya rulaa raha hai? kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Kisraa aur qaisar donon (kufr ke bawajood) us naaz w nemat mein hain jis mein hain aur aap to Allah ke rasool hain? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tumhen pasand nahi ke unke liye ( sirf ( duniya ho aur tumharey liye aakhirat ho?"
3693,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaid bin Hunain se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ( Haj se) wapas aaya yahan tak ke jab ham marruz-zohran mein they. aagey Sulaiman-bin Bilal ki hadis ki tarah poori lambi hadis bayan ki, magar unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : maine kaha : 2 aurton ka mamla kya tha? unhon-ne jawab diya : (wo ( Hafsa aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anhunna) ( thin) aur is mein ye izafa kya : main (pak beeviyon ke) hujron ke paas aaya to har ghar mein roney ki awaz thi, aur ye bhi izafa kya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse aik maah ela kya tha, jab 29 din huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( bula khaney se) utar kar unke paas tashrif ley aaey."
3694,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ubaid bin Hunain se suna, wo Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam they. unhon-ne kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se un 2 aurton ke barey mein poochhna chahta tha jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein ekaa kya tha, main saal bhar muntazir raha, mujhey koi munasib mauqa na mil raha tha, yahan tak ke main Makka ke safar mein unke sath gaya, jab ham Marruz-Zohran pahunchey to wo qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye gaey aur kaha : mere paas pani ka aik lota ley aana, maine unhein la diya. jab wo apni haajat se farigh ho kar lautey , main ja kar un (ke hathon ( par pani dalney laga, to mujhey ( sawal ( yad aa gaya, maine unse puchha : aey ameerul-momeneen ! wo kon si 2 auratein thin ? maine abhi apni baat khatm na ki thi ke unhon-ne jawab diya : wo Aaisha aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anhunna) thin."
3695,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin abi Sor se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main shiddat se khahish mand raha tha ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein se un 2 ke barey mein sawal karun jinke mutaalliq Allah Taala ne farmaya : agar tum donon Allah se tauba karti ho to yaqinan tumharey dil aagey jhuk gaey hain yahan tak ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Haj (ka safar ( kya aur maine bhi unke sath Haj kya, (wapsi par) ham rastey ke aik hissey mein they ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) (apni zarurat ke liye rastey se) aik taraf hat gaey aur main bhi pani ka bartan lene unke sath hat gaya, wo sehra mein chaley gaey, phir mere paas aaey to maine unke hathon par pani undela, unhon-ne wuzu kya to maine kaha : aey ameerul-momeneen! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein se wo 2 kon si thin jinke barey mein Allah Taala ne farmaya hai : agar tum donon Allah se tauba karo to yaqinan tumharey dil jhuk gaey hain? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Ibne-Abbas ! tum par tajjub hai ! . Zohri ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne jo sawal unse kya, wo unhein bura laga aur unhon-ne ( iska jawab ( chhipaaya bhi nahi. padhi. unhon-ne kaha : wo Hafsa aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anhunna) thin. phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) baat sunaney lagey aur kaha : ham Quraish ke log aisi qaum they jo apni aurton par ghalib they, jab ham Madina aaey to ham ne aisey log paaey jin par unki auratein ghalib thin, chunanche hamari aurton ne bhi unki aurton se seekhna shuru kar diya. (mardon ko palat kar jawab dene lagin.) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mera ghar oopri ilaaqey bani Umayya bin Zaid ke mahalley mein tha, aik din main apni biwi par naraz hua, to wo mujhey palat kar jawab dene lagi, mujhey iska jawab dena bada na-gawar guzra to usne kaha : tumhen ye na-gawar guzarta hai ke main tumhen jawab dun? Allah ki qism ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyan bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jawab de deti hain, aur unmein se koi aik to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko raat tak pura din chhod bhi deti hai (roothi rehti hai.) main chala, Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaya aur kaha : kya tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko palat kar jawab de deti ho? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan. maine (phir) puchha : kya tum mein se koi unhein raat tak din bhar ke liye chhod bhi deti hai? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan ! maine kaha : tum mein se jisne bhi aisa kya wo naakaam hui aur khasaarey mein padi. kya tum mein se koi is baat se be-khof ho jati hai ke apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki narazgi ki wjah se Allah ( bhi) is par naraz ho jaeyga to wo tabah w barbad ho jaeygi? (aainda) tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko na jawab dena, na unse kisi cheez ka mutalba karna, tumhen jo chahiye mujh se maang lena. tumhen ye baat dhokey mein na daal de ke tumhari hamsaai (saukan) tum se zyada khoobsurat aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zyada mehbub hai. unki murad Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se thi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Ansar mein se mera aik padosi tha. padhi. ham baari-baari (oopri ilaaqey se) utar kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hotey they. aik din wo utarta aur aik din main utarta, wo mere paas wahi wghaira ki khabrein laata aur main bhi (apni baari ke din) uske paas isi tarah ki khabrein laata aur (un dinon) ham aapas mein baatein kar rahe they ke ghassani hamarey sath ladai karne ke liye ghodon ko khadiyan laga rahe they, mera sathi ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir honey ke liye awaali se) utra , phir isha ke waqt mere paas aaya, mera darwaza khatkhataya, phir mujhey awaz di, main bahar nikla to usne kaha : aik bahut bada waqia roonuma ho gaya hai. maine puchha : kya hua? kya ghassani aa gaey? usne kaha : nahi, balke wo us se bhi bada aur lamba-chauda ( mamla) hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai. maine kaha : Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) to naakaam hui aur khasaarey mein pad gaee. main to (pahley hi) samajhta tha ke aisa honey wala hai. (doosrey din) jab main subah ki Namaz padh chuka to apne kapdey pahney , Madina mein aaya aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya, wo ro rahi thi. maine puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum sab ko talaaq de di hai? usne kaha : main nahi janti, albatta aap alag thalag us baala-khaaney mein hain. main aap ke siyah faam ghulam ke paas aaya, aur usey kaha, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye ijazat maango. wo gaya, phir meri taraf bahar aaya aur kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney tumhara zikr kya magar aap khamosh rahe. main chala aaya yahan tak ke member ke paas aa kar baith gaya, to wahan bahut se log baithey they, unmein se kuchh ro rahe they, mein thodi der betha, phir jo kaifiyat mujh par taari thi wo mujh par ghalib aa gaee. main phir ghulam ke paas aaya aur kaha : umr ke liye ijazat maango, wo andar dakhil hua, phir meri taraf bahar aaya aur kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney tumhara zikr kya, magar aap khamosh rahe. main peeth pher kar muda to achcha ghulam mujhey bulaney laga, aur kaha : andar chaley jao, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen ijazat de di hai. main andar dakhil hua, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam arz kya to dekha ke aap banti ki aik chataai par sahara lekar baithey they, jisne aap ke pahlu par nishan daal diye they, maine kaha : kya aap ne Allah ke rasool! apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai? aap ne meri taraf (dekhtey huey) apna sar Mubarak uthaya aur farmaya : nahi. maine kaha : Allahu-akbar . Allah ke rasool! agar aap hamein dekhtey to ham Quraish aisi qaum they jo apni beeviyon par ghalib rahtey they. jab ham Madina aaey to ham ne aisi qaum ko paya jinki auratein un par ghalib thin, to hamari aurton ne bhi unki aurton (ki aadat ( se seekhna shuru kar diya, chunanche aik din main apni biwi par barham hua to wo mujhey palat kar jawab dene lagi mujhey iska jawab dena intihai na-gawar guzra, usne kaha : tumhen ye na-gawar guzarta hai ke main tumhen jawab deti hun? Allah ki qism ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyan bhi aapko jawab de deti hain, aur unmein se koi to aapko raat tak chhod bhi deti (rooth bhi jati) hai. to maine kaha : unmein se jisne aisa kya wo naakaam hui aur khasaarey mein padi . kya (ye kaam karke ( unmein se koi is baat se be khof ho sakti hai ke apne rasool ki narazagi ki wjah se Allah is par naraz ho jaey (agar aisa hua) to wo tabah ho gaee. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskura diye to maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! main Hafsa ke paas gaya aur us ne kaha : tumhen ye baat kisi dhokey mein na daal de ke tumhari hamsaai ( saukan ( tum se zyada khoobsurat aur Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tum se zyada mahboob hai. is par aap dobara muskuraaey to maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! ( kuchh der baith kar) baat cheet karun? aap ne farmaya : haan. chunanche main baith gaya aur maine sar uper karke ghar mein nigah daudaai to Allah ki qism ! usmein teen chamdon ke siwa kuchh na tha jis par nazar padti, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! dua farmaiye ke Allah aap ki ummat par faraakhi farmaey. faarsiyon aur roomiyon par wusat ki gaee hai halanke wo Allah Taala ki ibadat nahi kartey. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) seedhey ho kar baith gaey, phir farmaya : ibne-khattaab ! kya tum kisi shak mein mubtala ho? ye aisey log hain jinhein un (ke hissey ( ki achi cheezein jald hi duniya mein de di gaee hain. maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! mere liye bakhshish talab kijiye aur aap ne un ( beeviyon ( par sakht ghussey ki wjah se qism kha li thi ke aik mahina unke paas nahi jaengey. yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne aap par itaab farmaya, (ke beeviyon ki baat par aap kyon ghamzada hotey aur halal chizon se door rehney ki qism khaatey hain. ("
3696,"Zohri ne kaha : mujhey Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : jab untees raatein guzar gain , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laaey, aap ne mere ( ghar ( se shuruaat ki, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap ne qism khaai thi ke mahina bhar hamarey paas nahi aaeingey, aur aap untiswein din tashrif laey hain, main unhein shumaar karti rahi hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah mahina untees din ka hai. phir farmaya : Aaisha ! main tum se aik baat karne laga hun, tumharey liye koi harj nahi ke tum apne waalidain se bhi mashwara karne tak usmein jaldi na karo. phir aap ne mere samney tilawat farmai : aey Nabi ! apni beeviyon se keh dijiye se lekar bahut bada ajr hai tak pahunch gaey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! aapko b-khoobi ilm tha ke mere waalidain mujhey kabhi aap se judai ka mashwara nahi dengey. kaha : to maine kaha : kya main iske barey mein apne waalidain se mashwara karungi? main yaqinan Allah, uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aakhirat ke ghar ki talabgaar hun. Mamar ne kaha : mujhey Ayub ne khabar di ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aap apni dusri beeviyon ko na bataein ke maine aapko chun liya hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : Allah Taala ne mujhey muballigh ( pahunchane-wala ( bana kar bheja hai, kamzoriyaan dhoondney wala bana kar nahi bheja. Qatada ne kaha : ( صَغَتْ قُلُوبُكُمَا Mina ( ) Tahreem : 4 : 66 (ka mana hai : tum donon ke dil maail ho chukey hain."
3697,"Aswad bin Sufiyan ke Maula Abdullah-bin Yazeed ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke abu Amr bin Hafs (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein talaaq bitta (hatami, teesri talaaq) de di, aur wo khud ghair hazir they, unke wakeel ne unki taraf se kuchh jau (wghaira) bhejey, to wo is par naraz huin, us ( wakeel ( ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! tumhara ham par koi haq nahi. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein, aur ye baat aapko batai. aap ne farmaya : ab tumhara kharch iske zimmey nahi. aur aap ne unhein hukm diya ke wo Umme- Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein iddat guzaarein, phir farmaya is aurat ke paas mere sahaba aatey jatey hain, tum ibne-maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan iddat guzar lo, wo na-beena aadmi hain, tum apne ( odhney ke) kapdey bhi utaar sakti ho. tum jab ( iddat ki bandish se) aazad ho jao to mujhey batana . jab main ( iddat se) farigh hui, to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataya ke Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan aur abu-Jaheem (Raziallahu anhu) donon ne mujhey nikah ka paigham bheja hai. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : abu-Jaheem (Raziallahu anhu) to apne kandhey se laathi nahi utaarta, aur raha Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) to wo intihai faqeer hai, uske paas koi maal nahi, tum Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kar lo. maine usey na-pasand kya, aap ne phir farmaya : Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kar lo. to maine unse nikah kar liya, Allah ne usmein khair daal di aur uski wjah se mujh par rashk kya janey laga."
3698,"abu-Hazim ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein unke shauhar ne unhein talaaq de di, aur us ne unhein bahut haqeer sa kharch diya, jab unhon-ne usey dekha to kaha : Allah ki qasam! main (is baat se) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zaroor aagah karungi, agar mere liye kharch hai to itna lungi jo meri guzraan durust kar de, agar mere liye kharch nahi hai to main us se kuchh bhi nahi lungi. unhon-ne kaha : maine is baat ka zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap ne farmaya : tumharey liye na kharch hai aur na rihaaish."
3699,"Imran bin abi Anas ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se malum kya to unhon-ne mujhey bataya ke unke makhzumi shauhar ne unhein talaaq de di aur un par kharch karne se bhi inkar kar diya, to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur aapko is baat ki khabar di to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey liye kharch nahi hai. ( wahan se) muntaqil ho kar ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan chali jao aur wahin raho, wo na-beena aadmi hain, tum wahan apne (odhney ke) kapdey bhi utaar sakogi."
3700,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se riwayat hai, (kaha :) mujhey abu-Salma ne khabar di ke Suhak bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki behen Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke abu-Hafs bin Mughira makhzumi (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey teen talaaqein de dein, phir Yaman ki taraf chala gaya, to iske azeez w aqaarib ne usey kaha : tumhara kharch hamarey zimmey nahi hai. Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) chand sathiyon ke sath aaey, Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : abu-Hafs ne apni biwi ko teen talaaqein de di hain, kya us (ki pichhli biwi (ke liye kharcha hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uske liye kharcha nahi hai jabke uske liye iddat ( guzaarna) zaroori hai. aur aap ne uski taraf paigham bheja : apne barey mein mujh se ( mashwara karne se pahley) sabqat na karna aur usey hukm diya ke Umme- Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan muntaqil ho jaey, phir usey paigham bheja : Umme- Sharik ke yahan awwaleen muhajireen aatey hain, tum ibne- Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan chali jao, jab (kabhi) tum apni odhni utaarogi to wo tumhen nahi dekh sakengey. wo unke yahan chali gain, jab unki iddat poori ho gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka nikah Usama-bin-Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) se kar diya."
3701,"Yahya bin Ayub, Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur ibne-Hujr ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ismail , yani ibne- Jafar ne Muhammad-bin Amr se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne hamein abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki. isi tarah hamein abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hadis bayan ki. (kaha : ( ham se Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( ham se Muhammad-bin Amr ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki : ( abu-Salma ne) kaha : maine Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke munh se sun kar ye hadis likhi, unhon-ne kaha : main banu- makhzoom ke aik aadmi ke yahan thi. usne mujhey teen talaaqein de dein to maine iske ghar walon ke yahan paigham bheja , main kharch ka mutalba kar rahi thi. padhi. aagey un sab ne abu-Salma se Yahya bin Kasir ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya, albatta Muhammad-bin Amr ki hadis mein hai : apne ( nikah ke) mamley main ( hamarey sath mashwara kiye baghair ( hamein peechhey na chhod dena."
3702,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf ne unhein khabar di ke Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke wo abu Amr bin Hafs bin Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi thin, unhon-ne usey teenon talaaqon mein se aakhiri talaaq bhi de di, unka khayal tha ke wo apne ghar se bahar nikalney ke barey mein fatwa poochhney ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin , to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke na-beena ( sahabi ( ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar muntaqil ho jaaein. Marwan ne (jab wo Madiney ka aamil tha) is baat se inkar kar diya ke wo mutallaqa aurat ke apne ghar se nikalney ke barey mein unki (baat ki) tasdeeq kare. aur Urwa ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bhi Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney is baat ko qabool karne se inkar kar diya."
3703,"Aqeel ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki, sath Urwa ka qaul bhi zikr kya ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke samney is baat ko naqabile-qabool qarar diya."
3704,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba se riwayat ki ke abu-Amr-bin-Hafs-bin-Mugheera (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Ali-bin-abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Yaman ki taraf gaey aur apni biwi Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ko uski (teen) talaaqon mein se jo talaaq baqi thi bhej di, aur unhon-ne unke barey mein (apne azeezon ( Haris-bin-Hisham aur Ayash-bin-abi-Rabee se kaha ke wo unhein kharch dein, to un donon ne un (Fatima) se kaha : Allah ki qism ! tumharey liye koi kharch nahi siwaey-iske ke tum haamla hoti . wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur aapko un donon ki baat batai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey liye kharch nahi (bantaa). unhon-ne aap se naql makaani ki ijazat chahi to aap ne unhein ijazat de di. unhon-ne puchha : Allah ke rasoo! kahan? farmaya : ibn-Umme-Maktoom ke yahaan. wo naa-beenaa they, wo unke samney apne ( odhney ke) kapdey utaartin to wo unhein dekh nahi saktey they. jab unki iddat poori hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka nikah Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se kar diya. iske baad Marwan ne us hadis ke barey mein malum karne ke liye qabeesa-bin-zuweb ko unke paas bheja to unhon-ne usey ye hadis bayan ki, is par Marwan ne kaha : ham ne ye hadis sirf aik aurat se suni hai, ham to usi maqbool tareeqey ko thaamey rakhengey jis par ham ne tamam logon ko paya hai. jab Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko Marwan ki ye baat pahunchi to unhon-ne kaha : mere aur tumharey darmyan Quraan faisal hai. Allah Taala ne farmaya : tum unhein unke gharon se mat nikaalo. aayat mukammal ki. unhon-ne kaha : ye aayat to (jis tarah iske alfaz ( لَعَلَّ ٱللَّہَ يُحْدِثُ بَعْدَ ذَٰلِكَ أَمْرًا ( ) الطلاق 1 : 65 )) se zahir hai) us ( shauhar (ke liye hui jisey rujoo ka haq hasil hai, aur teesri talaaq ke baad naye sirey se kon si baat paida ho sakti hai? aur tum ye baat kaisey kehtey ho ke agar wo haamla nahi hai to uske liye kharch nahi hai? phir tum usey roktey kis bana (wajah) par ho."
3705,"Zuhair-bin-Harab ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Hushaim ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein sayyaar, Husain, Mugheera, Ash'as, majaalid, Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid aur Dawud sab ne Shabi se khabar di. padhi. albatta Dawud ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. unhon-ne kaha : main Fatima-bint-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke faisley ke mutaalliq malum kiya jo unke barey mein tha. unhon-ne kaha : unke shauhar ne unhein teen talaaqein de dein, kaha : to main rihaaish aur kharch ke liye iske sath apna jhagdaa lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaee. kaha : to aap ne mujhey rihaaish aur kharch (ka haq ( na diya, aur mujhey hukm diya ke main apni iddat-ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar guzaaron."
3706,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hushaim ne Husain, Dawood, Mugheera, Ismail aur Ash'as se, unhon-ne Shabi se khabar di ke unhon-ne kaha : main Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya. padhi. ( aagey ( Hushaim se Zuhair ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah hai."
3707,"Qurra ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein sayyaar-abul-Hakam ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Shabi ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey, unhon-ne ibne-taab ki taaza khajooron se hamari ziyaafat (mahman nawazi) ki, aur hamein umda jau ke sattu pilaaey , iske baad maine unse aisi aurat ke barey mein puchha jisey teen talaaqein di gaee hon ke wo iddat kahan guzaarey gii? unhon-ne jawab diya : mujhey mere shauhar ne teen talaaqein dein to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ijazat di ke main apne gharaaney mein iddat guzaaron. ( ibne- Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) unke azeez they.)"
3708,"Salma-bin-kuheil ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne aisi aurat ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki jisey teen talaaqein de di gaee hon, aap ne farmaya : uske liye na rihaaish hai aur na kharch ."
3709,"yahyaa-bin-aadam ne hamein khabar di, (kaha : ( Ammar-bin-ruzaiq ne hamein Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere shauhar ne mujhey teen talaaqein dein to maine ( wahan se) naqle-makaani ka irada kiya. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui, to aap ne farmaya : tum apne chacha zaad Amr-bin-umme-maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar muntaqil ho jao, aur unke yahaan iddat guzaaro."
3710,"abu-Ahmad ne hamein khabar di, (kaha : ( Ammar-bin-ruzeiq ne hamein Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Aswad-bin-Yazeed ( Nakhai (ke sath ( Kufa ki) badi masjid mein betha hua tha, Shabi bhi hamarey sath they, to Shabi ne Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein rihaaish aur kharch (ka haq) nahi diya. phir Aswad ne muththi bhar kankariyaan lein aur unhein de maarein aur kaha : tum par afsos ! tum is tarah ki hadis bayan kar rahe ho? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha : ham aik aurat ke qaul ki wjah se Allah ki kitab aur uske rasool ki sunnat ko nahi chhod saktey, ham nahi jantey ke usne (is masley ko) yad rakha hai ya bhool gaee, uske liye rihaaish aur kharch hai. (aur ye aayat tilawat ki) izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : ''tum unhein unke gharon se na nikaalo, aur na wo khud nikleyn, magar ye ke wo koi khuli be hayaai kareyn."
3711,Sulaiman-bin-Muaz ne Abu-Ishaq se isi sanad ke sath Ammar-bin-razeeq se riwayat ki hui abu-Ahmad ki hadis ke ham mana hadis mukammal qissey samet bayan ki.
3712,"Wakee ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Abu-Bakar bin-abu-Jaheem-bin sikhkheer adwi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahi thin ke unke shauhar ne unhein teen talaaqein dein. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein rihaaish di na kharch. kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : jab ( iddat se) aazad ho jao to mujhey itlaa dena so maine aapko itlaa di. Muawiya , abu-Jaheem aur Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki taraf paigham bheja , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) to faqeer hai uske paas maal nahi hai, aur raha abu-Jaheem (Raziallahu anhu) to wo aurton ko bahut maarney wala hai, albatta Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) hai. unhon-ne (na-pasandidgi ka izhar kartey huey) hath se is tarah ishara kiya : Usama ! Usama ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein farmaya : Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki itaat tumharey liye behtar hai. kaha : to maine unse shadi kar li, iske baad mujh par rashk kiya janey laga."
3713,"Abdur-Rehman ne hamein Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Bakar-bin-abi-jaham se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahi thin : mere shauhar abu-Amr-bin-Hafs-bin-Mugheera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ayash-bin-abi-Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) ko meri talaaq ka paigham de kar bheja aur uske sath panch saa khajoorein aur panch saa jau bhi bhejey. maine kaha : kya mere liye sirf yahi kharch hai? kya main tum logon ke ghar mein iddat nahi guzaaron gi? us ne jawab diya : nahi. unhon-ne kaha : maine apne kapdey sametey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to aap ne puchha : wo tumhen kitni talaaqein de chukey hain? maine jawab diya : teen . aap ne farmaya is ne sach kaha, tumharey liye kharch nahi hai. apne chacha zaad Amr-bin-umme-maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar iddat guzaaro. wo naa-beenaa hain tum unke yahaan apna odhney ka kapda utaar sako gi . jab tumhari iddat khatm ho jaey to mujhey itlaa dena. unhon-ne ( aa kar) kaha : mujhey kai logon ne nikah ka paigham bheja hai, unmein Muawiya aur abu-Jaheem (Raziallahu anhu) bhi hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) to faqeer aur maflook (tabaahi) ki halat mein hai, aur rahe abu-Jaheem (Raziallahu anhu) to wo aurton par bahut sakhti kartey hain. padhi. ya wo aurton ko maartey hain, ya is tarah ki koi aur baat kahi . padhi. albatta tum Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko qabool kar lo."
3714,"abu-Aasim ne hamein khabar di (kaha : ( hamein Sufiyan-Sory ne Abu-Bakar-bin-abi-jaham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan hazir huey. ham ne unse sawal kiya, to unhon-ne kaha : main abu-Amr-bin-Hafs-bin-Mugheera (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi thi, wo Najran ki ladai mein nikley, aagey unhon-ne ibne- Mehdi ki hadis ke ham mana bayan kiya aur ye izafa kiya : ( Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : to maine un ( Usama (Raziallahu anhu)) se shadi kar li, Allah ne Abu-Zaid ( Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) ki wjah se mujhey sharf bakhshaa , Allah ne Abu-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki wjah se mujhey izzat di."
3715,"Shoba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( Abu-Bakar (bin-abi-jaham) ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aur abu-Salma, ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamane-khilafat mein, Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey to unhon-ne hamein hadis bayan ki ke unke shauhar ne unhein teen talaaqein dein, aagey Sufiyan ki hadis ki tarah hai."
3716,"( Abdullah-bin-Yasar) bahyee ne Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere shauhar ne mujhey teen talaaqein dein to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere liye rihaaish aur kharch nahi rakha."
3717,"Urwa-bin-Zubair ne kaha : Yahya-bin-Saeed-bin-aas ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Hakam ki beti se shadi ki, baad mein usey talaaq de di aur usey apne yahan se bhi nikal diya. Urwa ne is baat ki wjah se un par sakht aetraz kiya, to unhon-ne kaha : Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ( bhi apne khawind ke ghar se) chali gaee thi. Urwa ne kaha : is par main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unhein ye baat batai to unhon-ne kaha : Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye is hadis ko bayan karne mein koi khair nahi hai."
3718,"Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! mujhey mere shauhar ne teen talaaqein de dein hain, aur main darti hun ke koi ghus kar mujh par hamla kar dega, kaha : is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya to unhon-ne jagah badal li."
3719,"Shoba ne hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Qasim ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : is baat ko bayan karne mein Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke liye koi bhalai nahi hai ke na rihaaish hai na kharch."
3720,"Sufiyan ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se aur unhon-ne apne walid (Qasim) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya aap ne fulaana binte-Hakam ko nahi dekha? iske shauhar ne usey teen talaaqein dein to wo (uske ghar se) chali gaee. ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha is ne bura kiya. Urwa ne puchha : kya aap ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ka qaul nahi sunaa? to unhon-ne jawab diya : dekho ! usko bayan karne mein uske liye koi bhalai nahi hai."
3721,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : meri khala ko talaaq ho gaee, unhon-ne ( dauraane-iddat ( apni khajooron ka phal todney ka irada kiya, to aik aadmi ne unhein ( ghar se) bahar nikalney par daantaa. wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin , to aap ne farmaya : kyon nahi, apni khajooron ka phal todo, mumkin hai ke tum (is se) sadqa karo ya koi aur achchha kaam karo."
3722,"ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( mujhey Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah-bin-Utba-bin-Masood ne hadis bayan ki ke unke walid ne Umar-bin-Abdullah-bin-arqam Zohri ko hukm detey huey likha ke sabeeaa-binte-Haaris Aslamiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jayen, aur unse unke waqiey ke barey mein aur unke fatwa poochhney par jo kuchh Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya tha uske barey mein poochhein . chunanche Umar-bin-Abdullah ne Abdullah-bin-utba ko khabar detey huey likha ke sabeeaa ne unhein bataya hai ke wo Sad-bin-khaula (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi thin, wo bani Aamir-bin looie mein se they aur wo badr mein Shareek honey walon mein se they. wo Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par, faut ho gaey they jabke wo haamla thin. unki wafat ke baad zyada waqt na guzra tha ke unhon-ne bachchey ko janm diya. jab wo apne nifaas se paak huin to unhon-ne nikah ka paigham deney walon ke liye (ke unhein unki iddat se faraghat ka pata chal jaey kuchh) banao singhaar kiya. banu- abdud-daar ka aik aadmi . padhi. abu-Sanaabil-bin-ba'kak. padhi. unke yahaan aaya to unse kaha : kya baat hai main aapko bani sanwarii dekh raha hoon? shayad aapko nikah ki ummeed hai? Allah ki qism ! aap nikah nahi kar saktin yahan tak ke aap par char mahiney das din guzar jaaein. sabeeaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab usne mujhey ye baat kahi to Sham ke waqt maine apne kapdey sametey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur aap se iske barey mein malum kiya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey fatwa diya ke main usi waqt halal ho chuki hun jab maine bachcha janaa tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, agar main munasib samjhoon to mujhey shadi karne ka hukm diya. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : main koi harj nahi samajhta ke waza' hamal ke sath hi , chahey wo apne ( nifaas ke) khoon mein ho, aurat nikah kar ley , albatta uska shauhar uske paak honey tak uske qareeb na jaey."
3723,"abdul-wahaab ne kaha : maine Yahya-bin-Saeed se suna, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( mujhey Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ne khabar di ke abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) donon Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan ikatthey huey aur wo donon us aurat ka zikr karne lagey jiska apne shauhar ki wafat se chand raaton ke baad nifaas shuru ho jaey. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : uski iddat do waqton mein se aakhir wali hai. abu-Salma ne kaha : wo halal ho chuki hai. wo donon is mamley mein bahas karne lagey, to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main apne bhatijey, yani abu-Salma ke sath hun. iske baad unhon-ne is masley ke barey mein malum karne ke liye Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Kureb ko Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf bhejaa. wo (wapas ( unke paas aaya to unhein bataya ke Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha hai : sabeeaa Aslamiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne shauhar ki wafat se chand raaton ke baad bachcha janaa tha, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is baat ka zikr kiya to aap ne unhein nikah karne ka hukm diya tha."
3724,"Leis aur Yazid-bin-Harun donon ne isi sanad ke sath Yahya-bin-Saeed se riwayat ki, albatta Leis ne apni hadis mein kaha : unhon-ne ( kisi ko) Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf bhejaa. unhon-ne Kureb ka naam nahi liya."
3725,"Humaid-bin-Naafe ne Zainab-binte-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne in ( Humaid ( ko ye teen hadisein bayan kein, kaha : Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ke walid Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey to main unke yahaan gaee, Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne zard rang mili makhloot ya koi aur khushbu mangwaai , usmein se (pahley ( aik bachchi ko lagai (taake ( hath par uski miqdar bahut kam ho jaey) phir apne rukhsaaron par hath mal liya. phir kaha : Allah ki qism ! mujhey khushbu ki zarurat na thi magar ( baat ye hai ke) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap member par irshad farma rahe they : kisi aurat ke liye jo Allah Taala aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti ho, halal nahi ke wo kisi bhi marney waley par teen din se zyada sog manaaey, magar khawind par, char maah das din (sog manaaey)."
3726,"Zenab ( binte-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : phir main Zainab-binte-( Jahash ( (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan us waqt gaee jab unke bhai ( Ubaidullah-bin-Jahash ( faut huey, to unhon-ne bhi khushbu mangwaai aur lagai , phir kaha : Allah ki qism ! mujhey khushbu ki zarurat na thi magar ( baat ye hai ke) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap member par irshad farma rahe they : kisi aurat ke liye jo Allah par aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti hai, halal nahi ke wo kisi marney waley par teen din se zyada sog karey magar shauhar par, char mahiney das din (sog kare)."
3727,"Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine apni walida Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se suna wo keh rahi thin, aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! meri beti ka shauhar faut ho gaya hai. aur uski aankhon mein takleef hai. kya ham usey surma laga dein? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi do ya teen baar ( puchha gaya) har baar aap farmatey : nahi, phir farmaya : ye to sirf char maah das din hain. halanke jahiliyat main tum mein se aik aurat ( pura ( aik saal guzarney ke baad mengni phainkaa karti thi."
3728,"Humaid ne kaha : maine Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : aik saal guzarney par mengni phainknaa kya hai? Zenab ne jawab diya : ( jahiliyat mein) jab kisi aurat ka shauhar faut ho jata tha to wo aik ( dabdein numaa ( intihai tang jhounpdi mein chali jaati, apne badtareen kapdey pahan leti aur koi khushbu wghaira istemal na karti. yahan tak ke (isi haalat mein) saal guzar jata, phir uske paas koi janwar gadhaa , bakri ya koi parinda laya jata, to wo usey apni sharmgah se malti, kam hi hota ke wo kisi ko malti to wo zinda rehta ( sakht ta'ffun (badbu) aur jaraaseem wghaira ki bina par bimar ho kar mar jata) phir wo bahar nikalti to usey aik mengni di jati jisey wo (apne aagey ya peechhey) phainkti, phir iske baad khushbu wghaira jo wo chahti istemal karti."
3729,"Humaid-bin-Naafe se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Zainab-binte-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ka koi intihai qaribi azeez faut ho gaya. unhon-ne zard rang ki khushbu mangwai aur usey halka sa apne ( rukhsar aur) baazuon par lagaya , aur kaha : main isliye aisa kar rahi hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : kisi aurat ke liye jo Allah Taala aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti ho, halal nahi ke wo ( kisi marney waley par) teen din se zyada sog manaaey , magar khawind par char mahiney das din ( sog manaaey )."
3730,Zenab ne unhein ( Humaid ko) apni walida (Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ( se aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se ya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein se kisi se yahi hadis bayan ki.
3731,"Humaid bin Naafe se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Zenab binte- abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo apni walida se hadis bayan kar rahi thin ke aik aurat ka shauhar faut ho gaya, unhein uski aankh ke barey mein) bimari laahiq honey ka ( khatrah mehsus hua to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey, aur aap se surma lagaaney ki ijazat mangi , is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi apne ghar ke badtareen hissey main apne taaton mein. padhi. ya farmaya : apne badtareen taaton mein apne ghar ke andar . saal bhar rehti, iske baad jab koi kutta guzarta to wo aik leed phainkti aur bahar nikalti to kya ( ab ( char mahiney das din ( sabr ( nahi ( kar sakti .)"
3732,"Muaaz-bin-Muaaz ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Shoba ne Humaid bin Naafe se ikatthi 2 hadisein bayan kin, surma lagaaney ke barey mein Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki hadis aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein se aik aur biwi ki hadis , albatta unhon-ne unka naam , Zenab nahi liya. padhi. ( baqi hadis) Muhammad-bin-Jafar ki (pichhli ( hadis ki tarah ( bayan ki.)"
3733,"Humaid bin Naafe se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Zenab binte- abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Hazrat Umme-Salma aur Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahi thin, wo donon ye bata rahi thin ke aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir hui aur kaha ke uski aik beti ka shauhar faut ho gaya hai, uski aankh mein takleef ho gaee hai wo chahti hai ke usmein surma lagaey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah tum mein se koi aurat ( pura ( saal guzarney par leed phainka karti thi, aur ye to sirf char mahiney das din hain."
3734,"Zenab binte-abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : jab Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas (unke walid ( Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ki maut ki khabar aai to unhon-ne teesrey din zard rang ki khushbu mangwaai aur usey apne baazuon aur rukhsaaron par halka sa lagaya aur kaha : mujhey iski zarurat na thi, ( magar ( maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna tha : kisi aurat ke liye jo Allah Taala aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti ho, halal nahi ke wo ( kisi marney waley par) teen din se zyada sog manaaey , siwaey shauhar ke , wo is par char mahiney das din sog manaaey ."
3735,"Lais-bin-Sad ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Safiya binte- abi Ubaid ne unhein Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se ya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ya un donon se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi aurat ke liye, jo Allah Taala aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti hai. ya farmaya : Allah Taala aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par eman rakhti hai. halal nahi ke wo apne shauhar ke siwa kisi bhi marney waley par teen din se zyada sog manaaey ."
3736,Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Naafe se Leis ki hadis ki sanad ke sath usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat bayan ki.
3737,"Yahya-bin-Saeed kehtey hain : maine Naafe se suna, wo Safiya binte- abu-Ubaid se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hafsa binte- umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kar rahi thin. padhi. jis tarah Leis aur ibne- Dinar ki hadis hai. aur ye izafa kya : wo is par char mahiney das din sog manaaeygi."
3738,"Ayub aur Ubaidullah donon ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Safiya binte-abi-Ubaid se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kisi aur ahliya se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un ( Lais-bin-Sad , Abdullah-bin-Dinar aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ( ki hadis ke jaisi hadis riwayat ki."
3739,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : kisi aurat ke liye, jo Allah Taala aur qiyamat ke din par eman rakhti hai, halal nahi ke wo apne shauhar ke siwa kisi marney waley par teen din se zyada sog manaaey."
3740,"ibne-Idrees ne hamein Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aurat kisi marney waley par teen din se zyada sog na manaaey, magar khawind par, (us par) char mahiney das din (sog manaaey) na wo asab ke khaana daar kapdey ke siwa koi ranga hua kapda pahney, na surma lagaey, magar (is doran mein) jab ( haiz se) paak ho to mamuli si qust ya azfar ( jaisi koi cheez ( istemal kar ley. (ye donon khushbuein nahi, sirf badboo ko khatm karne waley b-khor hain)"
3741,"Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Yazid-bin-Harun, donon ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, aur donon ne kaha : tuhur ke shuruat mein thodi si qist aur azfar laga ley."
3742,"Ayub ne Hafsa se, unhon-ne umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein mana kya jata tha ke ham kisi marney waley par teen din se zyada sog manaaein . magar khawind par, (us par) char mahiney das din ( sog hai.) na surma lagaaein , na khushbu istemal karein aur na ranga hua kapda pahnein, aur aurat ko iske tuhur mein, jab ham mein se koi apne haiz se ghusl kar ley, ijazat di gaee ke wo thodi si qust aur azfar istemal kar ley."
